  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821090/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1739053786\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821090/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1739053786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821090/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1739053786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test your deduction skills and your tv series or streaming series knowledge</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821090/extras/526162ab5228027d361a25339e3282ba.avif?t=1739053786\" width=600 height=146 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >See plot summary of the series</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821090/extras/aa453ee3cce2ee6d349f36ef4076e3ac.avif?t=1739053786\" width=600 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some series are hard to guess</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821090/extras/9583dc60ef7706f5bf6f2d7d17d5d831.avif?t=1739053786\" width=600 height=188 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 100 series to guess.<br></li><li> Original soundtrack.<br></li><li> Minimalist interface.<br></li><li> Type the answer with keyboard or click in buttons with mouse.<br></li><li> Plot summary of the series.<br></li><li> It's pretty hard to guess alone all series.<br></li><li> Has hidden achievements...</li></ul>",
